Package: spotvolatility
Title: Estimate Spot Volatility
Version: 0.1
Author: Maarten Schermer, Kris Boudt, Jonathan Cornelissen
Maintainer: Maarten Schermer <m.j.a.schermer@gmail.com>
License: GPL-3
Description: The spotvolatility package offers several methods to estimate spot
    volatility and its intraday seasonality, using high-frequency data.
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.0),
    xts
Suggests:
    highfrequency,
    chron,
    timeDate,
    knitr
VignetteBuilder: knitr
LazyData: true
Thanks: Thanks to Roland Fried for kindly making his R code available to us,
    which has been helpful in the implementation of his piecewise constant
    volatility method in this package.
